@31 = ~Summon Devil Shade~
@32 = ~Summon Devil Shade

Devil Shades are amongst the most evil and vicious creatures, from the depths of the Abyss, to prey on the denizens of Faerun. They only appears at night and kills their prey by absorbing life force from their prey.~

@33 = ~Merge with shadows~
@34 = ~Merge with shadows

Merging with shadows allows the Shadow Ranger to become invisible immediately and makes them undetectable by divination spells such as True Sight. Only high level Shadow rangers can use this skill.~

@35 = ~Summon Fallen Deva~
@36 = ~Summon Fallen Deva

Range: 120 ft.
Duration: 4 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting time: 5
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: None

This spell opens an abyssal gate and calls forth a demonic deva to fight at the caster's side until the spell expires or the deva's earthly avatar is slain.~
